<li id="cite_note-2"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-2">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">See reviews of the <i>Linguasphere Register</i> by Edward J.Vajda in <i>Language</i> (Linguistic Society of America), Vol.77, 3 (Sept.2001) pp.606-608, and by Anthony P.Grant in <i>Journal of Royal Anthropological Society</i> (June 1, 2003).</span></li>
